text: MAT has an api so leak canary uses hoho (i think thats the lib) which just uses mat and runs shortest gc root excluding weak references

with that information leak canary just provides a simple UI.. normally this is a convoluted process of performing the heap dump, converting the heap dump to java format (it dumps in dalvik format), and then opening it in the eclipse MAT tool and finally knowing how to use the eclipse MAT tool
leak canary shortcuts all of that for you given most people are not likely to be aware of how to do all of those steps
